<!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.allthingsxena.com/Image_Gallery/Season%202/TQ/gifs/TQ_178.GIF"><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
<br>
*Qucikly, She swung her way closer to the landing and jumped down from the vines, she fell to her knees and caught her breath, but knew, sh eonly had seconds to get out. The walls trembled as she jumped to her feet and stumbled her way outside of the cavern, the amazon spirits were gone. Once outside, she fell again, taking the ambrosia out of the sachel when she had placed it. She held up a piece and thanked Hera and Artemis for there strength and protection in her quest.*<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.allthingsxena.com/Image_Gallery/Season%202/ANE/gifs/ANE_021.GIF"><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
<br>
*After her prayers, she injested the sweet ambrosia, a few pieces at a time, then slipped the rest into her sachel. She had a dizzying feeling come over her, she dropped to he rknees as a white light was engulfed around her.*<br>
<br>
